MG soft Inc. provides this Privacy Policy to explain our practices regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of information in connection with our website
https://www.iudesk.com
and our mobile application
Photo Editor
(together or individually “
Service
”) and other activities described in this Privacy Policy.
This Privacy Policy applies only to the practices of companies we own, control, or are united with under common control.
We use your data to provide and improve Service. By using Service, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy. Unless otherwise defined in this Privacy Policy, the terms used in this Privacy Policy have the same meanings as in
our Terms of Service.
Our Terms of Service (“
Terms
”) govern all use of our Service and together with the Privacy Policy constitutes your agreement with us (“
Agreements
”).
